Imagick::removeImageProfile

(PECL imagick 2.0.0)

Imagick::removeImageProfile — Removes the named image profile and returns it

Description

string Imagick::removeImageProfile ( string $name )
Warning

This function is currently not documented; only its argument list is available.

Removes the named image profile and returns it.

Parameters

name

Return Values

Returns a string containing the profile of the image. Throw an ImagickException on error.
